{#- ================================================================
ANALYZE_CHAPTER_USER.JINJA - Phase 0 : Analyse littéraire (User)

Purpose: User prompt for chapter analysis.
         First block: chapter text to analyze from scratch.
         Incremental: existing analysis + new text block to merge.

Input variables:
  - chapter_name       (str)
  - target_language    (str)
  - genre              (str, default: "fiction")
  Premier bloc (existing_analysis absent) :
    - chapter_text     (str)
  Incrémental (existing_analysis présent) :
    - existing_analysis  (str)   JSON de l'analyse partielle — active aussi le mode incrémental
    - current_block      (int)
    - total_blocks       (int)
    - chapter_text       (str)
    - is_last_block      (bool)

Pair: analyze_chapter_system.jinja
================================================================ -#}
{%- set is_incremental = existing_analysis is defined and existing_analysis -%}
{% if is_incremental %}
Chapitre : "{{ chapter_name }}" — Bloc {{ current_block }}/{{ total_blocks }}{% if is_last_block %} (dernier bloc){% endif %}

Analyse existante :
```json
{{ existing_analysis }}
```

Nouveau bloc de texte :

{{ chapter_text }}
{% else %}
Chapitre : "{{ chapter_name }}"

